<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Maha Tej Technologies | Engineering Pilot Programme</title>

<style>
body {
    font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: #FFFFFF;
    color: #111111;
    line-height: 1.7;
}

/* Container */
.container {
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 80px 0;
}

/* Hero */
.hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A3D62, #08334F);
    color: #FFFFFF;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 120px 20px;
}

.hero h1 {
    font-size: 38px;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
}

.hero p {
    font-size: 20px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: auto;
}

/* Buttons */
.btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 14px 34px;
    background-color: #F97316;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-top: 30px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.btn:hover {
    background-color: #0A3D62;
}

/* Section Titles */
h2 {
    color: #0A3D62;
    font-size: 28px;
}

h2::after {
    content: "";
    display: block;
    width: 70px;
    height: 3px;
    background-color: #F97316;
    margin-top: 12px;
}

/* Testimonials */
.testimonial {
    background-color: #F5F7FA;
    padding: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
    border-left: 4px solid #F97316;
}

/* Floating CTA */
.floating-cta {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 25px;
    right: 25px;
    background-color: #F97316;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    padding: 14px 22px;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: none;
    z-index: 999;
}

/* Fade In Animation */
.fade {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: all 0.8s ease-out;
}

.fade.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
}

/* Footer */
.footer {
    background-color: #111111;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
}

.footer a {
    color: #F97316;
    text-decoration: none;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero fade">
    <h1>Engineering Grade Airflow Optimisation for High Performance Tech Environments</h1>
    <p>
        The Maha Tej Technologies Pilot Programme delivers structured,
        simulation driven validation to identify cooling inefficiencies,
        reduce thermal risk, and build measurable performance clarity within three weeks.
    </p>
    <a href="#apply" class="btn">Reserve Your Pilot Position</a>
</section>

<!-- PROBLEM -->
<section class="container fade">
    <h2>Why This Matters</h2>
    <p>
        Many small and growing tech businesses rely on default cooling
        assumptions in server rooms and GPU environments.
        This results in pressure imbalance, recirculation zones, fan overcompensation,
        and escalating operational cost.
    </p>
    <p>
        The pilot programme establishes a quantified engineering baseline
        and provides structured optimisation scenarios supported by CFD modelling.
    </p>
</section>

<!-- WHAT YOU RECEIVE -->
<section class="container fade">
    <h2>What You Receive</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Three dimensional airflow and thermal distribution modelling</li>
        <li>Hotspot identification and pressure loss mapping</li>
        <li>Energy reduction scenario projections</li>
        <li>Prioritised engineering recommendations</li>
        <li>Executive summary suitable for internal review</li>
    </ul>
</section>

<!-- PROCESS -->
<section class="container fade">
    <h2>Structured Three Week Sprint Model</h2>
    <p><strong>Week 1:</strong> Baseline modelling and performance mapping</p>
    <p><strong>Week 2:</strong> Optimisation simulation and comparative analysis</p>
    <p><strong>Week 3:</strong> Validation report and implementation roadmap</p>
</section>

<!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
<section class="container fade">
    <h2>Early Validation Feedback</h2>

    <div class="testimonial">
        “The simulation outputs made the airflow imbalance obvious.
        We were able to make confident decisions rather than assumptions.”
    </div>

    <div class="testimonial">
        “Clear methodology. Transparent assumptions.
        The results were structured and credible.”
    </div>
</section>

<!-- APPLICATION -->
<section class="container fade" id="apply">
    <h2>Limited Intake</h2>
    <p>
        Only a small number of pilot partners are accepted each cycle
        to ensure technical depth and measurable outcomes.
    </p>
    <a href="mailto:your-email@example.com" class="btn">Apply for the Pilot</a>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer class="footer">
    <p><strong>Maha Tej Technologies</strong></p>
    <p>Engineering Led Simulation and Optimisation</p>
    <p>
        <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> |
        <a href="#">Terms of Service</a> |
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com">LinkedIn</a>
    </p>
</footer>

<!-- Floating CTA -->
<a href="#apply" class="floating-cta" id="floatingCTA">Reserve Your Pilot Spot</a>

<script>
const faders = document.querySelectorAll('.fade');
const options = { threshold: 0.2 };

const appearOnScroll = new IntersectionObserver(function(entries, observer) {
    entries.forEach(entry => {
        if (!entry.isIntersecting) return;
        entry.target.classList.add('visible');
        observer.unobserve(entry.target);
    });
}, options);

faders.forEach(fader => appearOnScroll.observe(fader));

window.addEventListener("scroll", function() {
    const cta = document.getElementById("floatingCTA");
    if (window.scrollY > 400) {
        cta.style.display = "block";
    } else {
        cta.style.display = "none";
    }
});
</script>

</body>
</html>
